hot-babe: hot-babe (Displays the system activity a very special way)
hot-babe:
hot-babe: hot-babe is a small graphical utility which displays the system
hot-babe: activity in a very special way. When the CPU is idle, it displays a
hot-babe: dressed girl, and when the activity goes up, as the temperature
hot-babe: increases, the girl begins to undress, to finish totally naked when
hot-babe: the system activity reaches 100%.
hot-babe: Of course, if you can be shocked by nudity, don't use it!
hot-babe:
